




         GFA Picture Displayer
         Version 5.1

         This is a short version of the Docs for Picture
         Displayer(PD).  PD is  a  program  written totally in GFA
         Basic that  allows  you  to display Low Resolution
         NeoChrome(tm) and Degas(tm) picture file in a slide show.  It
         has some feature's that other slide show's  dont have such as
         the ability to choose which drive you want to use  to display
         your picture files.  It also has the ability to use script
         files  which allow you to choose which file's  to  display.
         There will  be more feature's coming.  Let me know what ya
         think  about this so far.

         There are two files:
                            PicDisplay(Picture Displayer)
                            Scriptbl.bas(Script Builder program)

         Rich Noe
         Genie ID RNOE









































